Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.90,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}闔上雙目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.34,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.25,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:22.22,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的氣味 令人發狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:26.22,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}真夜中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:29.38,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}瘋狂 愛 一併飲乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:32.42,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}投入這臂彎中吧
